# Personal / third-party skills not tracked in this PUBLIC repo.
# Personal/PII skills now live in the private skillz-private plugin repo, not here.
# These two patterns are a backstop so a stray personal or aviz skill dropped into
# this dir isn't accidentally published.
almog-*/
aviz-*/

# Runtime state
.playwright-cli/

# Local notes
SKILLZ_NOTES.md

# Generated files inside tracked skills
ateam-apply/profile.md
ateam-apply/linkedin.pdf
ateam-apply/applied_missions.md

# Python bytecode
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
